div.container.container-error.mt-5
  h1
    if status === 404
      | Page Not Found
    else if status === 500
      | Something Went Wrong
    else
      | Error #{status}
  p
    if status === 404
      | The page you’re looking for doesn’t exist or has been moved.
    else if status === 500
      | An unexpected error occurred. Please try again later.
    else
      | Something went wrong.
  div.mt-2
    a.link.mt-3(href='/en-ca') Back to Home